/// New in 2.0 — per-execution work-time ledger ("dva skena": START + STOP).
/// Decomposes legacy tTehPostupak.DatumIVremeUnosa/DatumIVremeZavrsetka into an
/// append-only session ledger. tech_processes keeps the accumulated pieceCount;
/// a session's piece_count is that stop-scan's contribution (reconciled by construction).
